text: Joyraz Sheik (born 21 September 1996) is a Bangladeshi List A cricketer. In December 2015 he was named in Bangladesh's squad for the 2016 Under-19 Cricket World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Dhaka Category:Sheikh Jamal Dhanmondi Club cricketers Category:Old DOHS Sports Club cricketers Category:Dhaka Division cricketers Category:Bangladesh under-19 cricketers
